* Minimization and short dynamics of a solvated protein
* CHARMM input script
*

! Read topology and parameter files
open read card unit 10 name top_all36_prot.rtf
read rtf card unit 10

open read card unit 20 name par_all36m_prot.prm
read param card unit 20 flex

! Read protein structure
open read card unit 30 name protein.psf
read psf card unit 30

open read card unit 40 name protein.crd
read coor card unit 40

! Set up nonbonded options
nbonds atom cdiel eps 1.0 -
    cutnb 14.0 ctofnb 12.0 ctonnb 10.0 -
    switch vatom vswitch

! Energy minimization
mini sd nstep 200 nprint 50
mini abnr nstep 500 nprint 50 tolgrd 0.01

! Heating from 0 to 300 K
dynamics leap start timestep 0.002 nstep 5000 -
    nprint 100 iprfrq 1000 -
    firstt 0.0 finalt 300.0 -
    ihtfrq 100 teminc 5.0 -
    iasors 1 iasvel 1 iscvel 0 -
    ichecw 0 -
    nsavc 1000 nsavv 0 -
    iunread -1 iunwri 51 iuncrd 52 iunvel -1

! Write final coordinates
open write card unit 60 name protein_min.crd
write coor card unit 60

stop
